description: The associated files are mass spec data from size exclusion chromatography fractions that were subsequently crosslinked with DSSO.  The starting material was a native extract prepared from soy sprouts (Glycine max).  The mass spectrometry used a data-dependent MS2-MS3 method to identify crosslinks.
